{"tid":1324037,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[攬炒的味道] 港交所主席李小加指近期社會事件令國際投資者產生顧慮","createTime":"2019-07-16T12:30:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-16T12:48:20.000Z","uid":149494,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"decda54e39e04d13991bd5ca6555f3f30248d39c","tid":1324037,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T12:30:33.000Z","msg":"港交所(00388)行政總裁李小加表示, 本港一直充滿自由、開放、和平、寬容和理智, 但近日社會事件已令一些投資者, 產生顧慮和焦慮, 但所幸仍未「用腳投票」, 希望香港能遠離暴力、鎮壓和拘捕, 要拒絕絕望和悲觀, 互相容忍不同意見, 並認為政府會聆聽民意.<br />\n<br />\n        李小加表示, 正在尋找方案縮短新股結算周期, 由現時定價至上市最少五日, 即T+5, 縮短至T+1, 讓散戶和機構一樣, 不需要太早投入金錢, 但要先處理目前散戶優先的問題, 並指將在本月推出界內證, 相信能鞏固香港作為結構性產品的中心市場地位.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/default.aspx?NewsId=20190716103131\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.metroradio.com.hk%2Fnews%2Fdefault.aspx%3FNewsId%3D20190716103131&d=4wcocBccBPvk8MIeFEbr%2Bc70t8psI8cu6Rjg0MoA49o%3D&h=440b6289\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.metroradio.com.hk/news/default.aspx?NewsId=20190716103131</a><br />\n<br />\n延伸資訊︰本來係今年全球最大型IPO既百威上星期宣佈取消響香港上巿, 令香港新股巿場大受打擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">中產們, are you ready??</span></span>"},{"pid":"8558ddf878f9bf7ffa296b85095b77f974b0c50b","tid":1324037,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T12:35:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ee8a32b3b5fbf9110e5aa8f3e2d7649ed0641fd","tid":1324037,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T12:36:50.000Z","msg":"